      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Workflow / Execution Nodeset\n\nCandidate types from the source board:\n- `trigger`\n- `action`\n- `condition`\n- `transform`\n- `input`\n- `output`\n- `delay`\n- `state`\n- `branch`\n- `failure-handler`\n\nThis family only becomes real if Twilite wants inspectable execution graphs rather than static diagrams of workflow ideas.",
