      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Minimal Workflow Core\n\nApprove in v1:\n- `trigger`\n- `action`\n- `condition`\n- `input`\n- `output`\n- `branch`\n\nDefer:\n- `transform`\n- `delay`\n- `state`\n- `failure-handler`\n\nKeep v1 close to explicit execution flow.",
        "_classBinding": {
