      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Execution Pressures\n\nLikely mandatory semantics:\n- trigger starts action chain\n- condition gates branch choice\n- input/output carry payload shape\n\nRuntime pressure:\n- step status visibility\n- replay and inspection\n- branch outcome traces\n- error and retry surfaces\n- summary rollups for long-running workflows\n\nCurrent implementation slice landed:\n- `/library/classes/nodes/workflow-execution/root.node`\n- `/library/classes/nodes/workflow-execution/workflow-execution-template.node`\n- class artifacts for `trigger`, `action`, `condition`, `input`, `output`, and `branch`",
